Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.09,0:22:47.60,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,I must be losing my mind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.14,0:22:53.94,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,I keep on trying to find a way out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.94,0:23:00.49,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,But it's ok you don't lock the door anymore
